---
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-12">
  <div class="space-y-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-pink-200">Why Avatune?</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-4xl">Built for performance and developer experience</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-400/10">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Native Integration for High Performance</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Built directly for React, Svelte, Vue, and React Native, Avatune loads faster and runs smoother.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-400/10">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Instant SSR Rendering</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Avatars render immediately on the server — no waiting for images, perfect for SEO and fast TTFB.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-400/10">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Modular & Tree-Shakable</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Import only what you use, keeping your bundle lightweight and efficient.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-400/10">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Fully Type-Safe</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Designed with TypeScript end-to-end for a predictable, reliable developer experience.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-400/10">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Secure Browser-Only AI Predictions</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Hair, skin, and color predictions run locally in the browser, so user photos never leave the device.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-pink-400/10">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Flexible Across Frameworks</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Works seamlessly with React, Svelte, Vue, and React Native for easy UI integration.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
